{"data":[{"date":"14:51 16/06","title":"L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m BLV b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabregas b\u1ecb ch\u00ea nh\u01b0 ... b\u1ed3i b\u00e0n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/lan-dau-lam-blv-bong-da-tien-ve-fabregas-bi-che-nhu-boi-ban.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3654","checkdouble":"188639"},{"date":"14:59 16/06","title":"Hai sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1ee9c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i tr\u1ebb","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/hai-sao-tre-nguoi-anh-bi-bat-vi-cao-buoc-cuong-buc-co-gai-tre.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hai sao tr\u1ebb Reeco Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 Karlan Ahearne-Grant c\u1ee7a Charlton \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xxx m\u1ed9t c\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i.</h2>V\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 Ahearne-Grant \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1eaft \u1edf m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i Cala de Bou, g\u1ea7n khu ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t San Antonio t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3o Ibiza. Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/charlton.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ahearne-Grant \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u0169ng b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec nghi ng\u1edd ph\u1ea1m t\u1ed9i k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean nh\u01b0ng sau khi th\u1ea9m v\u1ea5n, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, Ahearne-Grant v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 qu\u00e1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i London v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1 v\u00e0 15 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn b\u1ecb gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecnh d\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i b\u1edfi theo lu\u1eadt T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00e1o tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd x\u00e9t x\u1eed t\u1ea1i t\u00f2a \u00e1n. Hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3o Ibiza v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ea7n/th\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i t\u00f2a \u00e1n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i, Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng l\u1ea1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u0129nh \u00e1n 15 n\u0103m t\u00f9.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecnh d\u1ee5c x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Hackett-Fairchild v\u00e0 Ahearne-Grant r\u1eddi qu\u00e1n bar Ocean Beach \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh b\u1edfi Wayne Lineker, anh trai c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Gary Lineker. C\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u201c\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0\u201d \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Charlton tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Cala de Bou. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 g\u00e1i 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1o c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t sau khi bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi con g\u00e1i h\u1ecd.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/charlton1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSau v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, CLB Charlton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o: \u201cCLB \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin v\u00e0 \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y. Do cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn th\u00eam g\u00ec v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y\u201d. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAhearne-Grant l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Charlton khi 17 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9/2014. Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 60 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CLB t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec Anh. Ahearne-Grant c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i cho U17, U18 v\u00e0 U19 Anh. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Hackett-Fairchild, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Charlton v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8/2017 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n trong 12 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3653","checkdouble":"188641"},{"date":"13:49 16/06","title":"T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n: Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u2018chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm\u2019 gi\u1eefa CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 n\u00e9m xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0103n m\u1eebng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/IMG_0792_resize.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, BTC s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a VFF. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, BTC tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 50.000.000\u0111 (N\u0103m m\u01b0\u01a1i tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng) do \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 13, di\u1ec5n ra ng\u00e0y 13/6/2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng do \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB SLNA v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 13, tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Vinh, Ngh\u1ec7 An.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1ea1 l\u00e2y b\u1edfi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c C\u0110V li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i d\u00f9 h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 hay s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u2018chung s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn ch\u1ecbu ph\u1ea1t\u2019 v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0 CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng song BTC s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ea1y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 n\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u chai, l\u1ecd xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u00ean s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay m\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u mai 17/6, v\u00f2ng 14 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3652","checkdouble":"188631"},{"date":"14:06 16/06","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-B.Binh-Duong-tai-Asiad-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o (s\u1ed1 3) l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 'm\u1eaft xanh' c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asiad 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi, trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i \u2018vi h\u00e0nh\u2019 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng kh\u1eafp c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e0i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean Thanh Th\u1ea3o v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, CLB B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ec3 VFF chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Thanh Th\u1ea3o c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. Vi\u1ec7c Thanh Th\u1ea3o l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00fd do g\u1ecdi Thanh Th\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i V.League 2018 v\u00e0 ghi 2 b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1 m\u0129 mi\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi bi\u1ebft tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi. Anh n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Song b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u mai 17/6, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thanh Th\u1ea3o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p SLNA t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong nh\u00f3m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang-168-188631.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tinh-trang-dot-phao-sang-tai-dien-nhieu-doi-bong-bi-phat-nang-168-188631.html\">T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n: Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\nBan k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3651","checkdouble":"188634"},{"date":"14:18 16/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u2018h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/them-mot-cau-thu-hang-thai-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, BL\u0110 CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/tien-ve-Hoang-Van-Binh-cua-FLC-Thanh-Hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Sau khi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hai v\u00e0 anh nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng SLNA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec h\u00f4m qua (15/6), \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh n\u0103m 1989 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef3nh L\u01b0u, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a v\u1edbi Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, \u00c2u V\u0103n Ho\u00e0n,\u2026 - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 SLNA t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2007... B\u1eb1ng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2011, Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 SEA Games. C\u0169ng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf SLNA, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng C\u00fap c\u00f9ng CLB (V.League 2011, C\u00fap QG 2010 v\u00e0 si\u00eau c\u00fap 2011).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a SLNA trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00a0Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3650","checkdouble":"188635"},{"date":"14:54 16/06","title":"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ean l\u1ec1 VCK World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Alfred Riedl \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>HLV Riedl: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 World Cup n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y!</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i U19 v\u00e0 U23 \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1, trong \u0111\u00f3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/1-1529073604-width500height333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Riedl kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a HLV Riedl th\u00ec ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi m\u00e0 su\u1ed1t 10 n\u0103m qua, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf \u0110TQG Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Zing.vn, \u00f4ng Riedl \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m qua. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn n\u00e0o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2007 v\u00e0 n\u0103m 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb khu v\u1ef1c. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t bao l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi C\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u01b0? \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Riedl ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t cho b\u00e0i to\u00e1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 10 n\u0103m qua ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 chung tay c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean th\u00ec gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi s\u1ed1 su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2026.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3649","checkdouble":"188640"},{"date":"16:12 16/06","title":"V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: Li\u1ec7u s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m m\u00f9a World Cup?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/14/vong-14-vleague-2018-lieu-suc-nong-co-giam-mua-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng 14 V-League di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u00edt nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tuy nhi\u00ean S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i n\u00ean r\u1eb1ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ngang c\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn play-off tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng ho\u1eb7c x\u1ea5u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 Khi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7t m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 Khi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7t m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/ha-noi-dai-thang-tai-vleague-da-den-luc-nghi-nghiem-tuc-ve-san-choi-chau-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Li\u1ec7u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m cho n\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u2018\u0111\u1ed9c c\u00f4 c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1i\u2019 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League v\u1edbi 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi 13 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea3 n\u1ed9i\u00a0 l\u1eabn ngo\u1ea1i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 14.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o l\u00e0 HAGL \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf Pleiku v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. Trong 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, HAGL \u0111ang gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Than Quang Ninh vs HAGL\" title=\"Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/sep-hagl-khong-hai-long-ve-hieu-suat-thi-dau-cua-cong-phuong-va-cac-dong-doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>CLB HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c l\u00e0 1-3 v\u00e0 0-1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, HAGL may ra m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn 6 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai 17/6. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, 16/6.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t h\u1eb3n l\u00ean nh\u00f3m an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC 2-1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn thua v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n, s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n, kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu m\u00e0 HLV H\u1ed3ng Vinh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u201cv\u0169 kh\u00ed\u201d c\u1ee7a XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 trong cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, sau\u00a0giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n V-League \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng\u00a0\u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t sau v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Thanh H\u00f3a l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean BXH, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i. Song li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng?</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"LTD vong 14 V-League 2018\" title=\"LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Vong-14-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#3a3a3a;background:#fafafa\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3648","checkdouble":"188647"},{"date":"14:46 16/06","title":"Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Alisson s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/29/chi-tiet-hop-dong-alisson-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, song n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i, Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Real s\u1ebd mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Courtois hay David de Gea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, De Gea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi MU, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Real ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nho-thuyet-khach-liverpool-sap-co-thu-mon-moi-172-187344.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9\u00a0th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio cung c\u1ea5p. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alisson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alisson, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u1ea1i Bernabeu Alisson s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 250.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng Real s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, song v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Real ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong khi Roma \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3647","checkdouble":"188633"},{"date":"13:10 16/06","title":"PSG chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng mua sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/psg-chi-so-tien-sieu-khung-mua-sao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua N'Golo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N'Golo Kante duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, sau khi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, PSG mu\u1ed1n mua NGolo Kante h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, PSG mu\u1ed1n mua NGolo Kante h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Chi-90-trieu-bang,-PSG-muon-mua-NGolo-Kante-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Blues, Kante c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n di chuy\u1ec3n trong 90 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, anh \u00e2m th\u1ea7m d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p m\u1ed1i nguy h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Kante l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Premier League \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Kante t\u1eeb Leicester, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Chelsea c\u00f3 2 danh hi\u1ec7u trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG chi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea-197-184021.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua N'Golo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span> nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" title=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/Chelsea-se-ban-Kante-cho-Real-Madrid-neu-co-Asensio-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG chi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua NGolo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Thiago Motta, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Mirror PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kante, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp cho m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, Kante s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nhan-don-dau-vu-sao-juventus-172-188630.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chelsea-nhan-don-dau-vu-sao-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nhan-don-dau-vu-sao-juventus-172-188630.html\">Chelsea nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao Juventus</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, song ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda PSG ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9. Hi\u1ec7n Kante \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga Les Bleus n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi \u00dac, Peru v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3646","checkdouble":"188620"},{"date":"14:00 16/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Danh t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Mario Gotze","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/16/day-danh-tinh-doi-bong-cua-nuoc-anh-sap-co-mario-gotze.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mario Gotze, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gotze mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mario Gotze b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho Dortmund, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mario Gotze v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mario Gotze v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/22/Tottenham-muon-mua-Mario-Gotze-voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gotze mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Bild c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Gotze \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Dortmund \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Gotze \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sao-dortmund-tha-thinh-liverpool-172-188137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gotze c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 c\u00f9ng Klopp \u1edf Liverpool</span>, Arsenal, Everton hay Newcastle c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Bayern tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh, Dortmund c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Gotze n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Gotze</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mario Gotze, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"mario gotze\" title=\"mario gotze\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/16/day-danh-tinh-doi-bong-cua-nuoc-anh-sap-co-mario-gotze.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Totteham mu\u1ed1n mua Gotze</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Gotze \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. HLV Pochettino \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Spurs.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Gotze s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Spurs c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3645","checkdouble":"188626"},{"date":"14:20 16/06","title":"Chelsea nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/21/chelsea-nhan-don-dau-vu-sao-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, song ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef Conte \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Daniele Rugani nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Daniele Rugani nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/chelsea-nhan-don-dau-vu-sao-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi m\u00e0 Gary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n David Luiz mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Rugani ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus v\u1edbi 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Rugani c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Chelsea tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chi-354-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-juventus-172-175920.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Daniele Rugani</span>, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rugani c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, song ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n David Torchia c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rugani\" title=\"Rugani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/17/mu-thach-thuc-arsenal-vu-hau-ve-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, c\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rugani l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u th\u00eam. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRugani c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o, Rugani h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Juventus v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDavid Torchia c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Juventus v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Rugani, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3644","checkdouble":"188630"},{"date":"09:11 16/06","title":"Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, khi ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1 vi\u00ean s\u1edf thu\u1ebf v\u1ee5 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo gian l\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2011-2014, ng\u00f4i sao kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>14,7 tri\u1ec7u euro</strong>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c v\u00ec gian l\u1eadn trong thu nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, khi d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ty ma \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra, thu th\u1eadp b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng. Nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span> di\u1ec5n ra, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1edd El Mundo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eadn t\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh th\u00eam chi ph\u00ed h\u1ea7u t\u00f2a, khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i <strong>t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 18,8 tri\u1ec7u euro.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn\" title=\"BDN Ronaldo lap cu dup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, <strong>CR7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n t\u00f9 2 n\u0103m. </strong>Th\u00f4ng tin t\u00edch c\u1ef1c duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u00e1n n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean vi ph\u1ea1m, Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo. Theo Lu\u1eadt, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 n\u0103m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh b\u1ed3i ho\u00e0n l\u1ea1i chi ph\u00ed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng thu\u1ebf c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u00ea chu\u1ea9n, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo 21 th\u00e1ng, do h\u00e0nh vi tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf <strong>4,1 tri\u1ec7u euro.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a CR7, khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;c\u1ea1nh tr\u1ea1nh&rdquo; v\u1edbi Lionel Messi tr\u00ean &ldquo;m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span><br>\r\nRonaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018. CR7 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N vs TBN, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3643","checkdouble":"188610"},{"date":"09:29 16/06","title":"M.U tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n De Gea th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nDe Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngay sau khi Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o David De Gea. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-180-188491.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson Becker</span> &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a AS Roma \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Real mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd l\u00e2u, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c M.U v\u00e0 David De Gea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford th\u00eam 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao De Gea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 350 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa\" title=\"De Gea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Edwin-van-der-Sar-phat-bieu-ve-David-de-Gea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. De Gea l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong c\u00fa hattrick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Man United l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua n\u00e0y. Cristiano \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng, l\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a HLV, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu-421-188610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-chinh-thuc-bi-ket-toi-tron-thue-doi-mat-2-nam-tu-421-188610.html\">Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, khi ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t La Roja h\u1ed7n mang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK World Cup 2018 ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Seleccao \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3642","checkdouble":"188612"}]}